      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="It is necessary to ensure that all systems feeding data into the general ledger (GL) contain consistent data records, such as account numbers. This will ensure that these feeder systems will reconcile and balance to the GL. This update feed should occur as often as data is fed into the GL, preferably on a real-time basis rather than overnight batches."/>
